<view class="feedback-page">
  <view class="feedback-nav">
    <view class="nav-back" bindtap="goBack">‹</view>
    <view class="nav-title">意见反馈</view>
    <view class="nav-spacer"></view>
  </view>

  <scroll-view class="feedback-scroll" scroll-y enhanced show-scrollbar="{{false}}">
    <view class="intro-card">
      <text class="intro-title">把不好用的地方告诉我们</text>
      <text class="intro-desc">可以写问题、建议、复现步骤，也可以附上截图。反馈会帮助兜兜有钱变得更顺手。</text>
    </view>

    <view class="form-card">
      <view class="field-head">
        <text class="field-title">反馈意见</text>
        <text class="field-required">必填</text>
      </view>
      <textarea
        class="feedback-textarea"
        value="{{content}}"
        maxlength="1000"
        placeholder="请描述你遇到的问题，或希望增加的功能"
        bindinput="onContentInput"
      />
      <view class="word-count">{{content.length}}/1000</view>
    </view>

    <view class="hint-card">
      <text class="hint-title">建议这样写</text>
      <text class="hint-text">1. 你正在做什么操作；2. 发生了什么问题；3. 你期望它怎么表现。截图可以帮助我们更快定位问题。</text>
    </view>
  </scroll-view>

  <view class="submit-bar">
    <view class="submit-btn {{submitting ? 'submit-btn--disabled' : ''}}" bindtap="submit">
      {{submitting ? '提交中...' : '提交反馈'}}
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
